```plantuml
@startuml FrogIT_Level1
skinparam backgroundColor #FEFEFE
skinparam component {
  BackgroundColor #E1F5FE
  BorderColor #0277BD
  ArrowColor #0277BD
}

actor "Desktop User" as User

package "FrogIT" #ALICEBLUE {
  component "FrogApp"           as FrogApp
  component "Frog"              as Frog
  component "ResourceManager"   as ResMgr
  component "SoundScape"        as Sound
  component "FrogSettingsUI"    as Settings
  database  "Constants"         as Const
}

package "External" #F3E5F5 {
  component "SFML Graphics" as SFML_G
  component "SFML Audio"    as SFML_A
  component "OS Desktop"    as OS
}

User  -down->  FrogApp : clicks / interacts
FrogApp -->    Frog
FrogApp -->    ResMgr
FrogApp -->    Sound
FrogApp -->    Settings
FrogApp -->    Const
Frog   -->     ResMgr
Frog   -->     Const

ResMgr  -down-> SFML_G
ResMgr  -down-> SFML_A
Sound   -down-> SFML_A
FrogApp -down-> SFML_G
FrogApp -down-> OS : transparent\nwindow

@enduml
```